thread.title: Tim D

author: Tim D
title: Tim D
text: I ordered as a new customer and was pleased with the call in service to clarify online questions. I found better selection and genuine knowledgeable service when I called for ordering. I would order again. I also found the selection of drivers I sought were better than other sellers. This the type of company and people we need in the industry to maintain excellence in service and selection in the competitive online market.
